{"tid":2043534,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"江峰时刻講香港獨立既可行方法","createTime":"2020-05-30T13:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T18:55:51.000Z","uid":160963,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b305c735689450bb88234c539715a0c8cacffab4","tid":2043534,"uid":160963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a1J5h9DcPUo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da1J5h9DcPUo&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=89b60fc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a1J5h9DcPUo</a><br />\n24:59開始聽<br />\n入面講到一但國安法正式實行香港會有30萬名英國公民要走佬<br />\n當中包括BNO人士, 但香港合資格BNO人士多達300萬, 英國咁細邊安排得到地方比BNO人士<br />\n所以UK依家頌有絕招係個一份放係聯合國既正本SBJD<br />\n一但公開宣佈中國破壞一國2制,中共在無合法管治區,<br />\n下1步中共一定會出兵,依一時刻因為中共在無香港管治權<br />\n所以美國出兵係保護同盟(香港)同埋保護自己國民走佬<br />\n其實香港要獨立建國成功一定係靠大國支持(USA)先生存到<br />\n另外一題既係香港本身地理位置除左係金融中心外,頌會係一個完美既軍事港,<br />\n可以直接對住深圳連同美國係亞洲設立既中國包圍網形成完美戰陣<br />\n另鯡一提依次國安法一出令好多對一國2制頌有FF既中立/淺黃明白到香港獨立先會有自治<br />\n想要真普選,共產黨到佢地黨解體都唔會比你<br />\n<br />\n希望大家睇完有冇D另類分析大家傾下"},{"pid":"e112d354608326ad7c057de1d052d2a8ec3b9586","tid":2043534,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有睇開...<br />\n不過佢都係冷軍多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc094153221437b2186752e6343c8ab97b4f569","tid":2043534,"uid":160963,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e112d354608326ad7c057de1d052d2a8ec3b9586","tid":2043534,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<